Package com.gdx.map

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FlagActor
    Actor class for putting markers on the GDXMap map stage.
    FlagWindow
    Creates new swing window for inputting information about the FlagActor on the map.
    GDXMap
    The main application of the program.
    HoverWindow
    Information Window containing market information
    InfoWindow
    Creates window which let's user search for specific FlagActors according to country, code and name.
    MapActor
    The Actor class which displays the actual map image on the GDXMap stage
    Window
    Abstract Window class, which should be used for all swing windows.
